Release Notes for Version 3.11.8
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.11.8 is the 9th release in
the Errata Tool 3.11 development period. It closes [37 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

Highlights of this release include a mechanism for automatically waiving rpmdiff
failures, grouping of errata into batches, and a redesigned advisory creation
form. Many small fixes and improvements are also included in this release.

